### SocialNet API Requests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### ==================== POSTS API ====================

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Create a new post
POST {{baseUrl}}/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Post",
  "content": "This is the content of my first post",
  "senderId": "user123"
}

### Get all posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/post

### Get posts by sender ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/post?sender=user123

### Get post by ID (replace with actual post ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/post/60d5ecb74e4d7a2d8c9b1234

### Update a post (replace with actual post ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/post/60d5ecb74e4d7a2d8c9b1234
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Post Title",
  "content": "Updated content for this post",
  "senderId": "user123"
}

### Delete a post (replace with actual post ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/post/60d5ecb74e4d7a2d8c9b1234

### ==================== COMMENTS API ====================

### Create a new comment (replace postId with actual post ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "This is a comment on the post",
  "postId": "60d5ecb74e4d7a2d8c9b1234",
  "senderId": "user456"
}

### Get all comments
GET {{baseUrl}}/comment

### Get comments by post ID (replace with actual post ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/comment?postId=60d5ecb74e4d7a2d8c9b1234

